## Description {#details}

A pair composed of a register and a sub-register index.

Used to give some type checking when modeling Reg:SubReg.

Definition at line 514 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/targetinstrinfo-h">TargetInstrInfo.h</a>.
